'''''Paigham''''' is a 1959 Hindi movie produced and directed by S S Vassan. The film stars [[Dilip Kumar]], [[Vyjayanthimala]], [[Raaj Kumar]],[[ Motilal (actor)| Motilal]] and [[Johnny Walker (actor)| Johnny Walker]]. The films music is by [[C. Ramachandra]]. This was the first time Dilip and Raaj Kumar appeared in a film together. They later appeared together once again over three decades later for the 1991 film ''[[Saudagar]]''.
==Awards==
[[Filmfare Best Dialogue Award]] for [[Ramanand Sagar]]
